    {"index":1,"name":"Ab Scissors","primary_muscle":"abdominals","other_muscles":[],"image_url":"https://d2l9nsnmtah87f.cloudfront.net/exercise-thumbnails/62141201-Lying-Scissors-Cross-(male)_Hips_thumbnail_@3x.jpg","instructions":"1. Sit on an exercise mat, lean back, and place your hands on the floor and to your sides for balance.\n2. Engage your abs and raise your feet several inches off the floor while keeping your knees extended.\n3. Take a breath and cross your legs by bringing the right one over the left. Immediately uncross them and move the left leg over the right.\n4. Keep alternating until you get tired, breathing steadily as you do reps.\n"},
